Copy everything below here into a new MDX file, using the naming structure established. Then drag that mdx file into the "posts" folder.

---
title: 'First Blog'
date: '18th April 2023'
publishedAt: '2025-01-02'
summary: 'store some links here'
description: Welcome to my first blog.
---
